value.0: The Obsidian Guard are renowned for their skill and are dangerously organized.

This helmet has been exquisitely forged from adamantine, its sinisterly beautiful design typical of drow craftsmanship. A small letter "V" has been interwoven into the pattern upon the visor.

Adamantine is an extraordinarily hard alloy that is almost impenetrable to normal weapons. Deposits of adamant are usually found near areas of Faerzress in the Underdark, and to the Deep Denizens it is usually black in colour, though it possesses a green sheen when viewed by natural light or a purple-white sheen when viewed by magical light.
